Version 1.1
------------
I want to thank Stephen Sawcer and Neil Walker for their help by reporting bugs on Windows. The pitfalls are now mentioned in the HOWTO file.

Fixed bugs
* --o Option now works properly
* call to an obsolete command removed, which used to issue an error message
* improved the documentation in the HOWTO file

New features
* The new sidline module allows you to draw graphs alongside chromosomes
* Multipage support added. The ideogram can now be split amongst several pages
* Added tableTools.pl to allow for file conversion from excel files.


